    "Conclusion and Future WorkThis study demonstrates that using LLMs to create cybersecurity exercise scenarios is both innovative and effective for training.",
    "The methodology effectively prepares security professionals to tackle a broad spectrum of cyber threats by simulating real-world challenges, encompassing both familiar and emerging cybersecurity issues.",
    "The integration of RAG adds depth and relevance to the scenarios, effectively utilizing LLM-generated content for more authentic simulations.",
    "Despite the critical scores in scenario 1, the overall quantitative measures provided us with good results.",
    "Future work should focus on further refining the integration of LLMs into cybersecurity training programs, particularly by expanding parameter coverage (LLMs with larger parameters) for more detailed scenarios and implementing generative configurations for increased creativity which will also assess the realworld impact of these scenarios on enhancing cybersecurity skills and readiness.Fig. 3:3Fig."
